OL,3,CHetty Pit: #300,000 project to restore
OL,4,Chistoric colliery site
OL,6,FA volunteer-led project to restore an
OL,7,Fhistoric colliery building near
OL,8,FPontypridd is taking a huge leap
OL,9,Fforward with more than #300,000 from
OL,10,Fthe National Lottery Heritage Fund.
OL,12,FThe money will refurbish the Hetty
OL,13,FPit's Grade 1 listed headframe, along
OL,14,Fwith installing a permanent air
OL,15,Fcompressor to power its winding engine
OL,16,Fand improvements for visitors.
OL,18,FOriginally part of Great Western
OL,19,FColliery, the Hetty shaft's steam
OL,20,Fwinder was installed in 1875.
