OL,3,CHetty Pit: #300,000 project to restore
OL,4,Chistoric colliery site
OL,6,FIn the mid 1990s, a team of
OL,7,Fvolunteers, led by Pontypridd Museum
OL,8,Fcurator Brian Davies, regained access
OL,9,Fto the site and began the process of
OL,10,Frestoring the winding engine to
OL,11,Fworking order.
OL,13,F"It's been 30 years of constant
OL,14,Fgradual improvement of the site, to
OL,15,Fmake it more visitor friendly and of
OL,16,Finterest to people" explains Aubrey
OL,17,FGreen, chair of the Great Western
OL,18,FColliery Preservation Trust.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/6
