OL,3,CHetty Pit: #300,000 project to restore
OL,4,Chistoric colliery site
OL,6,FThe new equipment means the winding
OL,7,Fengine can be operated more regularly,
OL,8,Fcontinuing to impress and educate
OL,9,Fvisitors to the site.
OL,11,FBut this year's progress is tinged
OL,12,Fwith an unavoidable sadness, due to
OL,13,Fthe death of Brian Davies in December
OL,14,F2023.
OL,16,F"It was a terrible shock" says friend
OL,17,FLen Smith.
